## Typography
Primary Font:
Helvetica Neue or Inter (sans-serif)
For headings and body text to maintain clarity and minimalism
Font weights: Light (300) for body text, Medium (500) for headings

Secondary Font:
Mono fonts like IBM Plex Mono or JetBrains Mono for code snippets or to emphasize important concepts
Weight: Regular (400)

Size Scale:
Base size: 16px (1rem)
Scale ratio: 1.25 (major third)
H1: 2.5rem
H2: 2rem
H3: 1.5rem
Body: 1rem
Small text: 0.875rem

## Color Palette
Primary Colors:
Off-white: #F7F7F7 (background)
Charcoal: #333333 (primary text)

Accent Colors:
Slate blue: #6B7A8F (subtle highlights)
Moss green: #7D8C6D (for links and interactive elements)
Terracotta: #C17767 (sparingly used for emphasis)

Functional Colors:
Light gray: #E5E5E5 (dividers, borders)
Medium gray: #BDBDBD (secondary text, inactive elements)

## Layout
Grid System:
12-column grid
Maximum width: 1200px
Generous whitespace: 32px minimum margins
Responsive breakpoints: 480px, 768px, 1024px, 1200px

Content Structure:
Asymmetrical layout with 2/3 main content, 1/3 sidebar
On mobile: single column, stacked layout
Card-based components with subtle shadows (2px blur, 30% opacity)

Spacing:
Base unit: 8px
Content padding: 24px
Section margins: 64px
Paragraph spacing: 16px

## Interaction & Motion
Transitions:
Subtle and purposeful
Duration: 200-300ms
Easing: Ease-out for entering elements, ease-in for exiting
No bounces or elastic effects (keeping with MUJI minimalism)

Hover States:
Minimal color shifts (10% darker/lighter)
Text links: No underline until hover
Buttons: Slight background color change, no dramatic effects

Scrolling:
Smooth scroll behavior
No scroll hijacking
Subtle fade-in animations for content as it enters viewport (150ms duration)

## UI Components
Navigation:
Minimal, fixed-position top navigation
No dropdown menus; use simple, flat navigation
Current page indicator: thin line under nav item (2px)

Buttons:
Minimal borders (1px)
Modest padding (16px horizontal, 8px vertical)
Text-only for secondary actions
No rounded corners (or very subtle 2px radius maximum)

Cards/Containers:
White backgrounds (#FFFFFF)
Very subtle borders (1px, #E5E5E5)
Minimal box shadows (2px blur, 4px y-offset, 5% opacity)
No rounded corners (or maximum 2px radius)

Images:
Desaturated by 10-15% to maintain cohesion with color palette
No rounded corners on images
Optional: subtle duotone effect using slate blue for visual consistency

## Content Display
Blog Posts:
Large, clear headings
Maximum line length: 70-75 characters
Line height: 1.6 for body text
Pull quotes in larger type (1.25rem) with left border accent (3px)
Code blocks with light gray background (#F1F1F1)

## Lab Entries:
Timestamp in small, lighter text (0.875rem, #BDBDBD)
Tags/categories with minimal styling (subtle background change only)
Reading time indicator

## Iconography
Thin line icons (1.5px stroke)
Monochromatic, using the charcoal primary color
Consistent size (24x24px)
No filled icons, only outlines
Minimal use - only where truly helpful for navigation

## Accessibility
Minimum contrast ratio: 4.5:1 for all text
Focus states clearly visible (2px border in accent color)
All interactive elements accessible via keyboard
Image alt text for all visual content

## Loading States
Minimal loading indicators
Prefer content skeleton loaders over spinners
No flashy animations during loading
